title: My Mom And Baby Daddy
itunes:title: My Mom And Baby Daddy
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I have known my baby daddy since high school. When I was 20, I got pregnant and we moved in together, but he cheated a lot, so when my son was 6, we broke up and my mom offered to let him live with her temporarily. My son is 16 now and my baby daddy still lives with my mom. My mom has 7 sisters that are very messy and they’ve always joked with my mom about having a fine young man living with her................
